responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "63F6F4A848DF04372800A7BC6B6780F8", "Of course we\'ve run into the Highwaymen outside the ruins, but to hear that they\'re actively recruiting our people is disheartening. I wonder how long it takes before they end up robbing their own friends or family?")
